### To activate Python Virtual Environemt

* Mac / Linux
```bash
source blog-env/bin/activate
```
* Windows Bash
```bash
source blog-env/Scripts/activate 
```
* Windows PowerShell
```bash
.\blog-env\Scripts\Activate.ps1
```

### To Deactivate Python Virtual Environment
``` bash
deactivate
```
----
### Run the Application
``` bash
uvicorn blog.main:app --reload
```